SUMMARY:Garage Con IV
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260530T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260530T220000
UID:ai1ec-148455-94948@wfhb.org
DESCRIPTION:Garage Con is back again after 7 years!Play board games\, card
  games\, RPGs\, and more all day. There will be game demos\, scheduled gam
 es\, or you can choose from the huge games library. Attendees are encourag
 ed to bring their own games to share as well. There will be plenty of spac
 e\, snacks & drinks for sale\, raffle prizes\, and\, of course\, tons of g
 ames to play all day… Come for a quickie or stay for some epic all-day g
 aming.How does Garage Con work?We love tabletop gaming\, so we’re bringi
 ng our board game collection and sharing with the community. Sign out a ga
 me to play with your friends or someone new. We’ll talk you through the 
 rules if you want to try a game you’ve never played before.
LOCATION:Bloomington Convention Center: 302 S College Ave
URL:https://wfhb.org/event/garage-con-iv/?instance_id=94948
